A cyberpunk digital fortress floating in a neon-drenched void, with streams of glowing cyan and magenta data particles flowing through transparent crystalline pathways that branch and merge like a complex maze. At the center, a geometric lock mechanism made of interlocking hexagonal shields pulses with energy, surrounded by orbiting fragments of encrypted code visualized as abstract golden geometric shapes. The atmosphere is thick with holographic grids and reflected light bouncing off dark chrome surfaces, creating depth and mystery. Rain-slicked surfaces below reflect the intense glow from above, while distant server towers rise like monolithic sentinels shrouded in digital fog.
